room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz" by Trapped In Decatur in Huntsville
room_description:
After getting involved with the wrong people, you end up in jail. A fellow inmate, trying to reduce his own sentence, falsely accuses you of murdering a guard. This extreme crime warrants your transfer to "The Rock", the supermax prison on Alcatraz Island.
One day, you receive a letter from brothers - they've developed a plan to break you out. You have 60 minutes to gather the necessary items and escape Alcatraz.
